Jim, Dave:
Sorry, the beams are different. 68-69 beams have a smaller footprint where they
bolt to the frame members and are actually interchangeable with 64-67.
Ya gotta change the spindles. But that's easier than changing beams anyway if
you know how. That beam is heavy and it's in there tight!
Al Brase
